    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207080/extras/616641c6720c215eebe8198a89b229a0.avif?t=1771755598\" width=1280 height=720 /></span>开普勒太空探索是一款真实的飞船轨道模拟游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的太阳系按比例构建，并以逼真图形呈现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，每个天体的运动都通过开普勒定律进行精确模拟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可通过组装各类部件打造专属火箭。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >飞我上月球</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先，让我们飞向月球，那皎洁的月球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是人类的一大步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有兔子。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207080/extras/d886984258af36e6c6090353ec0b4354.avif?t=1771755598\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >视频政策</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论个人或企业，均可无需事先许可进行游戏直播或发布视频。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对游戏内容展示范围及商业化运营均无限制。</p>",
